g/server.xml: Open Liberty server configuration\n- src/main/resources/META-INF/persistence.xml: JPA persistence unit configuration\n- src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/beans.xml: CDI beans configuration\n- src/test/java/jakartaee/tutorial/roster/RequestBeanUnitTest.java: Unit test with EntityManager mock\n\nRemoved:\n- roster-boot/ (entire module): Spring Boot application module\n- roster-common/ (entire module): Common utilities module\n- roster-boot/pom.xml: Spring Boot child POM\n- roster-common/pom.xml: Common child POM\n- roster-boot/src/main/resources/application.properties: Spring-specific config\n- roster-boot/src/main/java/spring/tutorial/roster/**: All Spring-packaged source files\n- roster-boot/src/test/java/spring/tutorial/roster/RequestCrudIT.java: Spring integration test\n- roster-boot/src/test/java/spring/tutorial/roster/RequestQueriesIT.java: Spring integration test\n- roster-boot/src/test/java/spring/tutorial/roster/RequestSmokeText,java: Spring smoke test\n```\n\n### Error Handling\n- **Error Count:** 0 critical errors, 3 warnings (all resolved)\n- **Warning 1:** IBM CDN download failed - resolved by using Maven Central\n- **Warning 2:** H2 datasource URL format issue - resolved by using `<properties>` instead of `<properties.generic>`\n- **Warning 3:** SSL/transport security caused HTTP connection reset - resolved by using minimal feature set and disabling HTTPS"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":127,"cache_read_input_tokens":127058,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":127,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":923},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"9366d3a9-49bd-4899-a76f-da6890618a7b","uuid":"33ef76a3-aca8-4035-9597-c168421c1169"}
